    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Moaba Leelisçhana pee Eſ-\nbosa newa wairs/ jo tee dohma\nlaunu prett winnu/ (fazzida-\nmi:) Nahzeet/ lai mehs to isdel-\ndam/ ka ta par Tantu wairs ne\neffoti. Ir tu/ ak Madmene!\ntapſi nozirſta/ tas Sohbins dſih-\nfees tew palkak.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Brehfschanas Balkfutē\nirr no Oronaima/ Pohſtifchana\nun leela Satreeſschana.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Moabs irr fatreefts/ win-\nna mast Behrni irr tikkuſchi wee-\nnu Kleegſchanu dsirdeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo augſchup uhs Lukitu\neet tee raudadanii/ un kur fein-\njup eet uhs Oronaimu/ irr tee\nGenaidneeki weenu Satreeſscha-\nnas Balkfut dsirdejschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Behdseet/ iſglabbeet juh-\nfas Dwehſeles/ bet tu buhſi ka\nSils Tuksnefi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tapehz ka tu uhs ta-\nwahm Ehkahm/ un uhs tawahm\nMantahm patanjes/ tapſi tu\narriſan uhsjenits/ un Ramos\naifees Zeetuma lihds ar taweem\nSwedtitajeem/ un jaweem Leel-\nKungeem kohpā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tas Pohſtitajs nahks\npahr ifkatru Pilſfahtu/ ka ne-\nmeens Pilſtahts ismiks/ un ta\nEeleija taps maitata/ un tas\nKlatimus taps pohstihts/ jo tas\nSirr to runnajs.\ndeet Moabam Spal-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nolahdehts lai irr ta-\nkas ta KUNGA Darbu ar W-\ntu darra/ un nolahdehts laid ir-\nkas jawu Sohbinu no Affi-\nIsleeſchanas aisturr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Moabs irr no jawas Ja-\nnibas bes Bihjaschanas biji-\nun irr uhs jawahm Meeleh-\nkluffu gullejs/ un ne irr no we-\nna Trauka eekſch ohtra pahrlce-\nun ne irr Zeetuma gahjs/ t-\npehz irr winnam jawu Sma-\npalikkuſi/ un winna Smars-\nne irr suddusi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz rangi/ tahs De-\nnas nahks/ taka tas KUNG-\nKa es pee ta Pahrdſinnejus fu-\ntitchu/ kas winnu pahrdſihs/\nwinna Traukus istuſchohs/\nwinna Blafchens ſadausihś.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ltn Moabs taps Kan-\npahr Kamofu/ itt ka tas Iſraē-\nNamē irr Kauna tappis pa-\nBeteli/ us ko tee patahwahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka warrefeet juhs fazzil\nMehs effam warreni un fi-\nWihti Karra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Moabs irr pohſtihts/\nwinna Pilſtahtōs irr wiſch-\nlahpis/ un winna ieveh-\nJaunekti irr pee Kaufchanas-\ngahluschi/ taka tas Rehnin-\nka Wahrdē irr KUNG-\nbaot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Bohja Gefchana M-\naba irr tuwu atnahkti/\nwi-\n"
    }
  ],
